
                                 FEAR::API
               There's no fear with this elegant site scraper

FEAR::API is a tool that helps reduce your time creating site scraping
scripts and help you do it in an much more elegant way. FEAR::API combines
many strong and powerful features from various CPAN modules, such as
LWP::UserAgent, WWW::Mechanize, Template::Extract, Encode, HTML::Parser,
etc. and digests them into a deeper Zen.

